name: Asylum - 33 - Toro
additionalNotes: Asylum 33 hails from the El Aladino factory in Danli, Honduras. This cigar is a Honduran puro that uses aged, premium 7 year old tobaccos resulting in a medium to full-bodied blend. You can expect your palate to be carpet bombed with flavors of red pepper, baking spices, chocolate, espresso, cream, wood, and leather. This stick is a slow burner with complexity, balance, and displays a pleasing evolution of flavors.Â
